attributionInfo.agentName: Jennie & Eddie Luxury Living Boston Team

description: Don’t miss out! Beautiful re-sale at the popular FP3 development in the desirable Seaport District. This ultra modern loft-style 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom unit totals 1,123 square feet and boasts an open floor plan with high ceilings, large windows and a sleek gourmet kitchen with Silestone counters and stainless steel appliances. Both bedrooms adjacent to luxury full baths. 2nd bedroom is interior. Full-service bldg with common roof deck, elevator, concierge, and easy rental parking nearby.
